26#include <sys/cdefs.h>
27__KERNEL_RCSID(0, "$NetBSD: nouveau_nvkm_engine_disp_g84.c,v 1.2 2018/08/27 04:58:31 riastradh Exp $");
28
29#include "nv50.h"
30#include "rootnv50.h"
31
32static const struct nv50_disp_func
33g84_disp = {
34 .intr = nv50_disp_intr,
35 .uevent = &nv50_disp_chan_uevent,
36 .super = nv50_disp_intr_supervisor,
37 .root = &g84_disp_root_oclass,
38 .head.vblank_init = nv50_disp_vblank_init,
39 .head.vblank_fini = nv50_disp_vblank_fini,
40 .head.scanoutpos = nv50_disp_root_scanoutpos,
41 .outp.internal.crt = nv50_dac_output_new,
42 .outp.internal.tmds = nv50_sor_output_new,
43 .outp.internal.lvds = nv50_sor_output_new,
44 .outp.external.tmds = nv50_pior_output_new,
45 .outp.external.dp = nv50_pior_dp_new,
46 .dac.nr = 3,
47 .dac.power = nv50_dac_power,
48 .dac.sense = nv50_dac_sense,
49 .sor.nr = 2,
50 .sor.power = nv50_sor_power,
51 .sor.hdmi = g84_hdmi_ctrl,
52 .pior.nr = 3,
53 .pior.power = nv50_pior_power,
54};
55
56int
57g84_disp_new(struct nvkm_device *device, int index, struct nvkm_disp **pdisp)
58{
59 return nv50_disp_new_(&g84_disp, device, index, 2, pdisp);
60}
